<p>Plato -&nbsp;</p>
<p>Necessity of philosophy in life.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Impact of education on nature of being .</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Without education, living in cave, experiencing world by shadow , when education by sun ,(reason) the outer world seems richer.&nbsp;</p>
<p>The man who got outside the cave cannot merely explain by words. It has to be learnt via experience.&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Role of culture h project phantoms (shadow) of fame, material world on our minds . Need to develop scientific temper and questioning.&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Process of education - method of enquiry and critical thinking to get out of cave (custom and traditions, change or keep, t understand their relevance today)</p>
<p>Wisdom starts owning of ignorance.&nbsp;</p>